Amend SS/Senate Bill No. 1553 , Pages 5-6 , Section 620.1641 , Lines 33-44 ,
2 by striking all of said lines and inserting in lieu thereof
3 the following:
4 "(8) "Qualified project costs":
5 (a) Costs incurred by a qualified company for the
6 construction, expansion, or conversion of facilities and
7 acquisition of equipment for the production of critical
8 materials or critical pharmaceuticals, including, but not
9 limited to:
10 a. Site preparation;
11 b. Building construction or renovation;
12 c. Machinery and equipment acquisition and
13 installation, including any specialized manufacturing
14 equipment;
15 d. Utility infrastructure; and
16 e. Environmental compliance systems;
17 (b) "Qualified project costs" shall not include any
18 costs incurred by a qualified company utilizing a contractor
19 unless:
20 a. Such contractor is selected through an open bidding
21 process and is headquartered in Missouri and for whom at
22 least eighty-five percent of the workforce used for any work
23 performed by the contractor for a qualified company reside
24 within fifty miles of the site of such work; and
